ing to guess.\n            print(f\"***********************YOU LOSE**********************\")\n            print(f\"The correct word is: {chosen_word}\")\n\n    if \"_\" not in display:\n        game_over = True\n        print(\"****************************YOU WIN****************************\")\n\n    # TODO-2: - Update the code below to use the stages List from the file hangman_art.py\n    print(hangman_art.stages[lives])\n"
